WEBVTT

02:13.220 --> 02:13.860
Look at me.

02:14.860 --> 02:15.300
What are you hiding from?

02:18.620 --> 02:19.019
Hello,

02:19.340 --> 02:20.620
is this the Linyuan District Police Station?

02:21.259 --> 02:22.060
There's a flasher

02:22.220 --> 02:22.900
in the alley

02:22.900 --> 02:23.699
near Suzhou No. 1 High School.

02:27.539 --> 02:28.940
Miss, just now...

02:30.739 --> 02:31.660
This alley isn't safe.

02:31.900 --> 02:32.579
Don't walk through it alone.

02:33.660 --> 02:34.060
Okay.

02:34.500 --> 02:35.380
Come with me. It's fine.

02:36.419 --> 02:36.739
Come on.

02:37.460 --> 02:37.819
Let's go.

02:44.220 --> 02:44.660
Alright.

02:44.660 --> 02:45.739
We've understood the situation.

02:46.139 --> 02:46.780
We'll arrange

02:46.780 --> 02:47.579
for someone to install

02:47.579 --> 02:48.259
the surveillance as soon as possible.

02:49.060 --> 02:49.819
But it'll take until tomorrow

02:49.819 --> 02:50.859
to connect the lines

02:51.299 --> 02:52.579
with the cooperation of all parties.

02:53.259 --> 02:53.859
Thank you.

02:54.139 --> 02:54.699
It's okay.

03:53.220 --> 03:53.819
Ruan Yu.

03:54.139 --> 03:54.900
Lawyer Xu.

04:01.819 --> 04:02.419
Are you okay?

04:02.979 --> 04:03.539
I'm fine.

04:15.139 --> 04:16.340
Why are you in Suzhou?

04:21.180 --> 04:22.180
I came back with my mom

04:23.259 --> 04:24.739
to clean up the old house

04:25.260 --> 04:26.220
and tidy up some stuff.

04:28.260 --> 04:28.979
Lawyer Xu,

04:29.660 --> 04:30.979
did you come back to see your family?

04:35.460 --> 04:38.179
Then why were you over there?

04:42.100 --> 04:42.979
I was just passing by.

04:43.499 --> 04:44.580
and heard about the accident.

04:44.900 --> 04:45.539
I came to see.

04:47.260 --> 04:48.900
He's also here for the accident.

05:00.660 --> 05:01.700
Is this all for dinner?

05:03.739 --> 05:04.619
I'm not hungry.

05:10.780 --> 05:11.660
Were you scared just now?

05:18.939 --> 05:19.739
Then why

05:20.939 --> 05:21.979
did you do it?

05:29.220 --> 05:30.179
So that people

05:30.859 --> 05:32.499
who walk that road won't be afraid anymore.

05:41.939 --> 05:42.780
But next time

05:43.340 --> 05:44.660
if you encounter something like this,

05:45.379 --> 05:45.939
you'd better

05:48.780 --> 05:50.100
mind your own business.

05:51.140 --> 05:51.660
Find someone

05:52.660 --> 05:54.859
to mind business with you.

06:11.460 --> 06:12.299
They both

06:13.820 --> 06:15.059
lost their memories, right?

06:16.820 --> 06:17.739
They don't look like

06:18.820 --> 06:20.539
they just met each other.

06:25.979 --> 06:26.580
Hello, boss.

06:29.020 --> 06:30.220
Young man, it's you.

06:31.179 --> 06:31.979
What a coincidence.

06:32.140 --> 06:32.900
That girl,

06:33.700 --> 06:34.460
the girl

06:35.900 --> 06:36.580
is here.

06:36.900 --> 06:37.619
Do you remember?

06:37.979 --> 06:38.619
I don't.

06:38.700 --> 06:39.020
You...

06:39.100 --> 06:39.700
You go ahead.

06:39.820 --> 06:40.460
I'll go read.

06:41.220 --> 06:41.820
What?

06:44.979 --> 06:47.619
You don't remember her?

06:48.700 --> 06:49.379
So,

06:49.619 --> 06:50.340
I'm just

06:50.340 --> 06:51.020
overreacting?

06:56.379 --> 06:59.220
It's still a long way to go.

07:15.539 --> 07:19.220
For example, going to the police station.

07:26.260 --> 07:27.539
What are you thinking about, Ruan Yu?

07:27.539 --> 07:28.179
Wake up.

07:28.700 --> 07:30.179
Xu Huaisong, this is the Law Channel,

07:30.179 --> 07:31.059
not the Romance Channel.

07:36.379 --> 07:37.619
I went to the police station

07:37.859 --> 07:39.379
this afternoon.

07:46.179 --> 07:47.619
Why did you come to No. 1 Middle School?

07:52.539 --> 07:54.340
I was just wandering around.

07:54.859 --> 07:56.100
And I ended up here.

07:57.539 --> 07:58.020
Well,

07:58.539 --> 07:59.260
Lawyer Xu,

07:59.580 --> 08:00.900
why don't you spend the festival

08:00.900 --> 08:01.580
with your family?

08:04.660 --> 08:05.739
I don't celebrate these festivals.

08:08.220 --> 08:08.900
That makes sense.

08:10.100 --> 08:11.660
There are no such festivals abroad.

08:16.739 --> 08:17.499
Lawyer Xu,

08:19.660 --> 08:20.939
did you go abroad

08:21.780 --> 08:22.939
right after high school?

08:29.780 --> 08:30.739
Why did you choose

08:32.220 --> 08:34.020
to study abroad at that time?

08:39.619 --> 08:40.379
It was arranged by my family.

08:43.940 --> 08:45.540
Wasn't it your own choice?

08:47.619 --> 08:49.100
Did you want to go yourself?

08:53.940 --> 08:55.139
It was my choice too.

08:56.940 --> 08:57.700
But if...

09:08.700 --> 09:09.379
No buts.

09:23.460 --> 09:24.340
It's getting late.

09:24.899 --> 09:25.859
When are you heading back to Hangzhou?

09:28.180 --> 09:28.779
I'll just stay

09:28.779 --> 09:30.180
at the old house tonight.

09:31.220 --> 09:32.379
I'll go back

09:32.379 --> 09:33.180
after tomorrow's matter

09:33.340 --> 09:33.899
is completely resolved.

09:37.019 --> 09:37.899
I'll give you a ride later.

09:38.580 --> 09:39.060
No, thanks.

09:39.340 --> 09:40.180
Don't bother.

09:41.060 --> 09:41.859
Safety first.

10:01.259 --> 10:01.979
Family arrangement?

10:03.180 --> 10:04.019
I told you,

10:04.019 --> 10:04.979
I don't have this son.

10:05.619 --> 10:06.700
He's not my family.

10:07.019 --> 10:08.739
If you want to go, go by yourself.

10:09.700 --> 10:10.619
Liar.

10:11.659 --> 10:12.619
Mom.

10:17.060 --> 10:18.540
It seems he doesn't get along well

10:19.139 --> 10:20.220
with his mom.

10:23.420 --> 10:25.420
Is there any other reason

10:29.659 --> 10:31.220
for him to go abroad?

10:32.220 --> 10:33.499
I chose it myself.

10:34.420 --> 10:35.259
But if...

10:42.940 --> 10:43.580
No if.

10:49.220 --> 10:49.739
Forget it.

10:51.420 --> 10:52.700
There is no if anyway.

10:54.100 --> 10:55.060
What's the point

10:55.739 --> 10:56.739
of asking these?

11:16.220 --> 11:18.379
The suspect of the murder case of a female college student in Su City

11:19.060 --> 11:20.700
was acquitted.

11:21.499 --> 11:24.100
[Victims' families seek justice.]

11:26.460 --> 11:27.180
Stop it.

11:27.859 --> 11:29.379
Stop it and do your homework.

11:36.899 --> 11:37.779
Even if you finish it today,

11:37.779 --> 11:39.139
there will be more tomorrow.

11:40.659 --> 11:41.420
I'll paint them all

11:41.659 --> 11:42.739
red later.

11:44.019 --> 11:45.220
If you want to work on this case,

11:45.499 --> 11:46.499
don't come home.

11:47.379 --> 11:48.899
You're being unreasonable.

12:04.220 --> 12:05.940
Wasn't it your choice?

12:07.859 --> 12:09.499
Do you want to go there yourself?

12:38.779 --> 12:40.259
It's raining so hard again.

12:42.899 --> 12:44.340
Will I be stuck here again today?

12:48.139 --> 12:49.420
Why isn't anyone taking the order?

13:09.779 --> 13:11.659
Sister Ruan Yu, it's really you.

13:11.659 --> 13:12.540
What are you doing here?

13:13.019 --> 13:14.540
Why is it these two again?

13:15.340 --> 13:15.940
I...

13:16.139 --> 13:17.779
I'm just about to go to the train station.

13:17.820 --> 13:18.739
To the train station?

13:18.739 --> 13:19.180
Right.

13:20.139 --> 13:21.420
We're just on the way.

13:21.420 --> 13:22.220
Why don't you get in?

13:22.220 --> 13:23.019
We can give you a ride.

13:23.739 --> 13:24.300
No, thanks.

13:24.300 --> 13:25.739
I'm calling a car.

13:25.739 --> 13:26.940
The driver should be here soon.

13:27.340 --> 13:28.220
The rain is too heavy.

13:28.220 --> 13:29.220
Come on in.

13:33.100 --> 13:34.460
We can't stop for long. Get in.

13:35.739 --> 13:36.340
Thank you.

13:44.940 --> 13:45.659
Just put it anywhere.

13:47.139 --> 13:47.820
Sorry.

13:49.100 --> 13:49.779
Seat belt.

13:51.499 --> 13:52.100
Bro,

13:52.619 --> 13:54.060
The gentleman in the novel

13:54.060 --> 13:54.979
always fastens the seat belt

13:54.979 --> 13:55.979
for the heroine.

13:56.540 --> 13:57.180
I'm fine.

13:57.180 --> 13:57.979
I can do it myself.

14:02.899 --> 14:03.420
Thank you.

14:09.940 --> 14:10.899
It's the weekend.

14:11.259 --> 14:12.580
Why are you near the school?

14:14.580 --> 14:16.180
We're shopping.

14:16.820 --> 14:17.619
My brother said

14:17.619 --> 14:19.420
there are bad guys around the school,

14:19.899 --> 14:20.700
so I should take a detour.

14:21.019 --> 14:22.460
So he's showing me the way.

14:25.220 --> 14:26.379
Even though he's been caught,

14:26.659 --> 14:28.019
we still need to be vigilant.

14:30.700 --> 14:32.700
So he drove around

14:32.700 --> 14:34.700
for an hour,

14:35.379 --> 14:36.779
finally waiting for the person to pick up.

14:38.100 --> 14:40.659
The Xu siblings have a lot of tears of sorrow.

14:41.899 --> 14:43.060
Take her home first,

14:43.379 --> 14:44.580
then we'll go straight back to Hangzhou.

14:46.619 --> 14:47.420
Lawyer Xu,

14:47.619 --> 14:48.460
you can go back too.

15:04.300 --> 15:05.220
Are you chatting, bro?

15:05.659 --> 15:06.700
Say something.

15:07.100 --> 15:07.820
Sister Ruan Yu

15:07.820 --> 15:09.259
likes a cool guy,

15:09.259 --> 15:10.779
not a dumb guy.

15:15.340 --> 15:16.940
You're so talkative.

15:17.220 --> 15:18.139
But when it comes to the point,

15:18.220 --> 15:19.580
you still need me to liven things up.

15:21.540 --> 15:22.259
Sister Ruan Yu,

15:23.499 --> 15:23.940
did you come

15:23.940 --> 15:25.139
to our school yesterday?

15:28.460 --> 15:29.899
Zhao Da said that

15:30.060 --> 15:31.100
a writer came

15:31.340 --> 15:32.379
visited our school yesterday.

15:32.460 --> 15:33.820
He met her when he was playing soccer.

15:34.259 --> 15:34.940
It was you, right?

15:36.300 --> 15:36.899
Zhao Da,

15:41.060 --> 15:41.979
what's your name?

15:42.340 --> 15:42.899
Zhao Yi.

15:43.979 --> 15:45.700
Che Shiyi, not iron.

15:46.580 --> 15:47.460
[Zhao Yi?]

15:48.420 --> 15:50.060
[He's Xu Huashi's classmate.]

15:51.139 --> 15:52.499
[Good thing I didn't say much.]

15:55.019 --> 15:56.899
I was just hanging out.

15:59.180 --> 16:00.139
But our school

16:00.139 --> 16:01.659
doesn't allow hanging around.

16:02.340 --> 16:04.019
Sis, how did you get in?

16:07.060 --> 16:07.700
I...

16:09.899 --> 16:11.259
Maybe the security guard wasn't paying attention,

16:11.739 --> 16:13.659
or thought I looked harmless.

16:15.619 --> 16:17.060
Smooth talker.

16:17.739 --> 16:18.420
No wonder my brother

16:18.420 --> 16:19.580
can't find a way to come clean.

16:22.940 --> 16:23.540
Sis,

16:23.820 --> 16:25.180
you've come to No. 1 Middle School,

16:25.340 --> 16:26.859
why didn't you come to play with me?

16:28.460 --> 16:29.540
Xu Huashi, do you think

16:29.540 --> 16:31.100
everyone has as much free time as you do?

16:31.820 --> 16:33.060
If you can't hold back your words,

16:33.499 --> 16:34.220
recite the text.

16:44.300 --> 16:45.019
Sister,

16:45.379 --> 16:46.180
where did you get

16:46.180 --> 16:47.300
that canvas bag?

16:49.379 --> 16:50.180
It's a gift from my friend.

16:52.019 --> 16:54.180
What kind of friend do you have?

16:54.739 --> 16:56.700
This is the same model as Shican's.

16:56.899 --> 16:57.779
He often carries it

16:57.779 --> 16:58.979
when he attends activities.

17:02.859 --> 17:04.460
Are you a fan of Li Shican?

17:05.659 --> 17:07.019
I remember this bag

17:07.100 --> 17:09.060
is a limited edition.

17:09.259 --> 17:09.859
Sister,

17:09.859 --> 17:11.420
who is your friend?

17:11.420 --> 17:12.459
He's amazing.

17:12.459 --> 17:13.500
Xu Huashi

17:13.859 --> 17:14.379
Sister,

17:14.899 --> 17:16.659
are you also a fan of Shi Can?

17:17.139 --> 17:17.740
Do you have any

17:17.740 --> 17:18.459
special channels?

17:18.459 --> 17:19.619
Can you share with me?

17:19.619 --> 17:21.340
Xu Huashi, do you study these

17:21.659 --> 17:22.580
at school?

17:23.500 --> 17:24.899
I'm not falling behind in my studies.

17:25.139 --> 17:25.459
Don't talk nonsense.

17:25.459 --> 17:27.179
It's just a hobby.

17:27.179 --> 17:28.100
It's a good way to relax.

17:28.859 --> 17:29.619
Besides,

17:29.699 --> 17:30.500
Li Shican

17:30.899 --> 17:32.580
is a positive role model, right?

17:33.419 --> 17:34.419
Exactly.

17:34.540 --> 17:35.260
He's very

17:35.260 --> 17:36.980
positive

17:37.060 --> 17:38.980
in both work and life.

17:39.139 --> 17:40.179
He's full of energy,

17:40.179 --> 17:40.980
and brings positive vibes

17:40.980 --> 17:42.619
to his fans.

17:43.179 --> 17:44.179
Even Sister Ruan Yu

17:44.179 --> 17:45.060
was drawn to him.

17:45.379 --> 17:47.139
Bro, I knew

17:47.139 --> 17:48.179
I was right about him.

17:48.500 --> 17:49.980
He's really outstanding

17:50.139 --> 17:51.740
and worth learning from.

17:53.580 --> 17:54.100
That's not

17:54.100 --> 17:55.219
a reason for you to

17:55.219 --> 17:56.260
waste your family's money on him.

17:59.939 --> 18:01.179
No wonder Xu Huaisong

18:01.179 --> 18:02.500
is so hostile to Li Shican.

18:03.260 --> 18:04.340
I see.

18:08.179 --> 18:09.379
We're almost there.

18:09.699 --> 18:10.980
Get ready to get off

18:10.980 --> 18:11.699
with your mouth.

18:29.980 --> 18:30.859
Slow down.

18:31.699 --> 18:32.540
It's so big.

18:35.580 --> 18:36.100
Be careful.

18:37.740 --> 18:38.820
Goodbye, sister.

18:38.980 --> 18:39.580
Goodbye.

18:39.580 --> 18:40.340
Goodbye, brother.

19:27.939 --> 19:29.300
Li Shican's song.

19:42.139 --> 19:43.459
Is the novel back on track?

19:46.540 --> 19:47.260
Not yet.

19:49.740 --> 19:51.020
Still struggling to get into the right mindset.

19:52.260 --> 19:53.260
Or just no inspiration?

19:54.459 --> 19:56.619
Maybe it's been paused too long.

19:57.699 --> 19:59.179
Hard to pick up where I left off.

20:06.219 --> 20:07.379
If it hadn't been paused,

20:07.899 --> 20:09.459
what would the ending

20:09.820 --> 20:10.859
of your novel be?

20:14.580 --> 20:15.179
It's...

20:21.340 --> 20:22.619
It's the main characters'

20:24.060 --> 20:27.300
a graduation trip after the college entrance exam.

20:37.980 --> 20:38.899
Let me see.

20:40.939 --> 20:41.260
Ruan Yu,

20:41.260 --> 20:42.379
didn't you already sign up?

20:43.419 --> 20:44.260
I'm just checking

20:44.419 --> 20:45.699
who else is going.

20:49.899 --> 20:50.899
Xiaofei, your phone number.

20:50.980 --> 20:51.459
Look,

20:51.459 --> 20:52.300
188

20:53.540 --> 20:54.459
2571

20:54.459 --> 20:55.020
188...

20:55.899 --> 20:57.219
I see he signed up too.

21:01.020 --> 21:03.459
Are you sure you want to confess?

21:05.260 --> 21:06.580
Traveling with another class,

21:07.060 --> 21:08.100
what a great opportunity!

21:09.820 --> 21:11.300
Whether he's studying abroad or not,

21:11.619 --> 21:12.740
whether he has someone he likes or not,

21:13.659 --> 21:14.659
as long as he's single,

21:15.100 --> 21:16.179
I, at eighteen,

21:16.179 --> 21:17.340
have the right to confess.

21:18.340 --> 21:19.020
I've thought it through.

21:19.540 --> 21:20.580
No matter the outcome,

21:21.780 --> 21:22.939
I want to give my youth

21:23.459 --> 21:24.179
a proper closure.

21:37.619 --> 21:39.740
Ruan Yu, here.

21:49.820 --> 21:50.459
Stop it.

21:50.459 --> 21:50.980
Stop looking.

21:50.980 --> 21:51.780
He hasn't come yet.

21:52.780 --> 21:53.300
Not yet?

21:54.100 --> 21:55.379
What's the gift?

22:15.139 --> 22:16.260
Why so many stars?

22:16.580 --> 22:17.740
It represents the 1,013 days

22:17.740 --> 22:18.740
of our high school life.

22:19.139 --> 22:20.020
Not a single one can be missing.

22:22.219 --> 22:23.139
It took her over a week

22:23.500 --> 22:24.899
to fold over a thousand paper stars.

22:25.379 --> 22:27.580
Love is truly powerful.

22:29.619 --> 22:30.980
Look, is it okay?

22:33.580 --> 22:34.340
Perfect.

22:36.500 --> 22:37.379
Why hasn't he come yet?

22:37.740 --> 22:38.179
He should be here soon.

22:38.459 --> 22:39.020
Guys,

22:39.379 --> 22:40.980
we're all here now.

22:40.980 --> 22:41.820
Get ready to board the bus.

22:42.580 --> 22:44.300
Monitor, everyone's here.

22:45.419 --> 22:47.419
Monitor, what about Xu Huaisong?

22:47.899 --> 22:48.699
Xu Huaisong?

22:48.780 --> 22:50.260
The one from Class 10.

22:52.300 --> 22:53.459
Xu Huaisong isn't coming?

22:54.379 --> 22:55.820
He's probably not interested

22:55.820 --> 22:56.580
in group activities.

22:56.859 --> 22:58.139
Zhou Jun, get on the bus.

23:02.340 --> 23:03.340
You two, hurry up.

23:03.340 --> 23:04.540
There are still seats in the front.

23:04.740 --> 23:05.500
Alright, hurry up.

23:06.020 --> 23:06.699
So,

23:07.419 --> 23:08.859
he has no attachment

23:09.379 --> 23:10.699
to anyone here?

23:11.540 --> 23:12.379
Should we get on the bus first?

23:45.580 --> 23:46.980
Xu Huaisong isn't coming?

23:47.659 --> 23:49.100
He probably doesn't like

23:49.100 --> 23:49.820
group activities.

23:49.820 --> 23:52.419
The summer graduation trip

23:52.659 --> 23:53.219
of Class 9 and 10, Grade 12,

23:53.219 --> 23:54.699
Suzhou No.1 High School,

23:54.699 --> 23:56.820
Class of 2014, is about to begin.

23:57.379 --> 23:58.619
I hope we can

23:58.619 --> 24:00.659
create beautiful memories

24:00.659 --> 24:02.179
in the last group activity.

24:02.379 --> 24:04.379
Happy graduation.

24:07.580 --> 24:08.939
Okay, fasten your seat belts.

24:08.939 --> 24:09.780
We're about to set off.

24:29.139 --> 24:30.100
In that trip,

24:31.100 --> 24:32.100
the heroine

24:32.100 --> 24:34.379
prepared a confession.

24:34.820 --> 24:37.020
But she didn't wait

24:37.020 --> 24:37.980
for the hero.

24:40.619 --> 24:42.699
So the heroine's

24:42.699 --> 24:44.219
confession was doomed

24:44.780 --> 24:45.740
not to be heard

24:46.340 --> 24:47.859
from the beginning.

24:48.740 --> 24:50.340
The gift she prepared

24:51.260 --> 24:52.419
was doomed

24:52.820 --> 24:54.219
not to be given.

24:58.179 --> 24:59.500
Does it sound a little cruel?

25:07.540 --> 25:08.899
But for the heroine,

25:09.659 --> 25:11.100
the absence of the hero

25:11.899 --> 25:12.899
actually gives her

25:12.899 --> 25:14.100
an answer.

25:15.820 --> 25:17.340
It should be a happy ending.

25:22.939 --> 25:23.619
Why?

25:24.540 --> 25:25.540
In this world,

25:26.500 --> 25:27.780
the hardest thing to heal

25:28.419 --> 25:29.659
is never a broken heart,

25:30.659 --> 25:31.580
but unrequited love.

25:32.740 --> 25:33.859
Because in unrequited love,

25:34.740 --> 25:36.060
who have never been rejected

25:36.820 --> 25:37.899
will always have the right

25:38.379 --> 25:39.740
to fantasize about the ending,

25:41.500 --> 25:44.659
so they will always tie themselves up in knots.

25:45.419 --> 25:47.060
But once they muster up all their courage

25:47.060 --> 25:47.899
to try,

25:48.820 --> 25:50.300
they will be completely crushed.

25:50.859 --> 25:54.340
Then the secret love will turn into

25:54.540 --> 25:55.899
a curable heartbreak.

25:56.939 --> 25:57.740
The world is big,

25:58.619 --> 25:59.699
and the years are long,

26:01.139 --> 26:04.540
the heroine will let go of the hero.

26:18.139 --> 26:18.780
Lawyer Xu,

26:19.179 --> 26:20.020
you seem to be speeding.

26:27.540 --> 26:28.260
Readers

26:28.820 --> 26:30.219
won't accept this ending.

26:31.740 --> 26:32.540
Maybe.

26:35.100 --> 26:38.100
But the endings of some stories

26:39.340 --> 26:40.659
are already predestined.

26:42.060 --> 26:42.939
Creators

26:44.780 --> 26:46.459
may not be able to change much.

27:17.580 --> 27:18.260
Mom,

27:19.820 --> 27:21.419
I'm fine. I didn't get wet.

27:21.500 --> 27:22.780
I'm already home now.

27:25.020 --> 27:25.980
I didn't take the high-speed train.

27:26.300 --> 27:29.260
I met a friend on the way.

27:31.020 --> 27:31.500
Okay.

27:32.540 --> 27:33.980
Then you and dad should get some rest early.

27:35.300 --> 27:35.859
Good night.

27:42.740 --> 27:43.740
Hasn't he left yet?

28:14.260 --> 28:17.580
Love only lasts forever in regrets.

28:23.100 --> 28:24.179
Perhaps many years later,

28:24.820 --> 28:26.020
she will meet him again.

28:26.580 --> 28:27.619
But by the time they meet,

28:28.659 --> 28:30.179
the heart might have already been worn away

28:30.179 --> 28:31.780
by the worries of life and time.

28:32.580 --> 28:34.699
Love is eternal in regret.

28:55.100 --> 28:55.820
Yeah.

28:56.219 --> 28:57.379
In the world literature,

28:57.859 --> 28:59.139
tragedies

28:59.139 --> 29:00.340
are more unforgettable.

29:01.060 --> 29:02.899
Why should we change the ending?

29:22.500 --> 29:23.340
The world is so big,

29:24.540 --> 29:25.540
and time is so long.

29:26.899 --> 29:30.300
The heroine will let the hero go.

30:18.260 --> 30:19.419
Glutinous rice is hard to digest,

30:19.740 --> 30:21.500
so I didn't put it in.

30:22.659 --> 30:24.340
It may taste a little bit bad.

30:24.980 --> 30:27.780
Just make do with it.

30:33.020 --> 30:33.899
It's authentic.

31:10.980 --> 31:11.580
Lawyer Xu,

31:12.260 --> 31:13.379
I switched to Suzhou's

31:13.379 --> 31:14.179
pork fat rice cake.

31:14.419 --> 31:15.340
You probably don't

31:15.340 --> 31:16.459
get to eat this abroad, right?

31:17.899 --> 31:18.379
Thank you.

31:35.459 --> 31:35.939
[Brother,]

31:36.100 --> 31:36.899
[have you arrived?]

31:37.260 --> 31:37.899
[Remember to hold an umbrella]

31:37.899 --> 31:39.379
[for Sister Ruan Yu when you get off.]

31:39.580 --> 31:40.179
Rainy days

31:40.179 --> 31:42.020
are perfect for getting closer.

31:42.139 --> 31:43.300
Make sure to take advantage of it.

31:46.619 --> 31:47.139
What if

31:47.139 --> 31:48.580
there's no chance to hold an umbrella?

32:09.659 --> 32:10.419
Don't worry,

32:10.939 --> 32:12.500
I won't give up.

32:13.020 --> 32:14.300
Just give me some time

32:14.939 --> 32:16.020
to plan.

32:17.580 --> 32:18.459
The lawsuit

32:18.699 --> 32:19.899
is almost over.

32:20.419 --> 32:21.780
And what about you and Xu Huaisong?

32:22.139 --> 32:23.300
come to an end too?

32:23.980 --> 32:24.699
Of course.

32:25.939 --> 32:27.179
After the case is over,

32:27.899 --> 32:29.659
he should go back to the US.

32:31.419 --> 32:33.219
That sounds like a good thing.

32:33.459 --> 32:35.219
You won't have to worry about

32:35.219 --> 32:37.100
being exposed or embarrassed anymore.

32:39.379 --> 32:40.780
What's with the sigh?

32:41.260 --> 32:43.859
Do you kind of miss him?

32:45.020 --> 32:46.219
Did I just sigh?

32:48.379 --> 32:49.179
Alright.

32:50.619 --> 32:52.619
Maybe it's because I talked about

32:52.619 --> 32:53.899
about the ending of the novel,

32:56.500 --> 32:57.820
I was also hurt.

33:00.340 --> 33:01.260
It seems that my prophecy

33:01.260 --> 33:02.820
of your old love

33:02.820 --> 33:04.379
is coming true step by step.

33:05.980 --> 33:08.179
This is at most a recurrence of old wounds.

33:08.980 --> 33:10.859
Isn't it scary?

33:10.859 --> 33:12.219
I tell you,

33:12.219 --> 33:13.740
you are now in the play for art.

33:13.740 --> 33:16.060
It's easy for you to get into the play but hard to get out of it.

33:16.419 --> 33:17.419
Did you forget

33:17.419 --> 33:18.100
how long it took you

33:18.100 --> 33:19.100
to forget him?

33:19.300 --> 33:19.859
That was...

33:20.219 --> 33:21.780
That was after college, wasn't it?

33:21.780 --> 33:23.100
You still think of him from time to time.

33:23.780 --> 33:25.219
He is now

33:25.219 --> 33:27.260
entering your life again,

33:27.260 --> 33:28.340
and leaving again.

33:28.899 --> 33:30.219
Back then, I didn't even get to see him

33:30.219 --> 33:31.139
one last time.

33:31.740 --> 33:32.300
That's why

33:32.300 --> 33:33.699
I've been dwelling on it for so long.

33:35.540 --> 33:36.419
This time,

33:38.219 --> 33:39.500
I'll say a proper goodbye.

33:41.060 --> 33:42.340
Then I'll be fine.

33:42.780 --> 33:43.820
How to say a proper goodbye?

34:10.260 --> 34:11.260
No, no, no.

34:11.859 --> 34:13.020
Take a break.

34:14.139 --> 34:15.100
Did you

34:15.780 --> 34:16.860
get upset at his place?

34:16.860 --> 34:18.380
You're clearly taking it out on me.

34:18.380 --> 34:19.339
Come on, bring it on.

34:19.699 --> 34:20.299
I'm done.

34:28.619 --> 34:29.100
Do you two

34:29.100 --> 34:30.179
have any misunderstandings?

34:32.980 --> 34:33.659
Misunderstanding?

34:36.020 --> 34:36.580
When I was in the hospital,

34:36.580 --> 34:37.540
she visited me

34:37.540 --> 34:38.420
and brought me porridge.

34:38.819 --> 34:39.739
Was that also a misunderstanding?

34:40.299 --> 34:41.580
Wasn't it you who sent her a WeChat message

34:41.580 --> 34:42.699
and asked her to come over?

34:43.139 --> 34:44.219
What about the fried rice cake?

34:45.659 --> 34:47.100
Didn't you say you were hungry?

34:48.339 --> 34:48.900
Yes.

34:49.580 --> 34:50.580
Everything you just said

34:50.580 --> 34:51.819
was something I begged for.

34:52.259 --> 34:53.540
I was just being too hopeful.

34:56.020 --> 34:56.699
Yeah.

34:59.860 --> 35:00.659
No, wait.

35:02.580 --> 35:03.420
But,

35:04.819 --> 35:05.420
I can

35:05.420 --> 35:07.060
give you some advice now.

35:07.580 --> 35:08.619
You always told me

35:08.619 --> 35:09.739
to stop being

35:09.739 --> 35:11.339
too hopeful.

35:11.900 --> 35:13.940
I've learned a lot.

35:16.420 --> 35:17.100
Listen,

35:18.060 --> 35:18.699
don't

35:19.580 --> 35:21.060
don't get too stuck in your ways.

35:21.659 --> 35:22.900
What's wrong with free candy?

35:23.380 --> 35:25.259
Does it lose its sweetness?

35:26.380 --> 35:28.219
If you get it, just enjoy it first.

35:28.500 --> 35:29.900
Finish it before you worry.

35:30.339 --> 35:30.819
Right?

35:31.900 --> 35:32.739
It's not like

35:32.739 --> 35:34.339
you're being overly hopeful.

35:36.420 --> 35:37.259
Just don't rush.

35:38.219 --> 35:39.299
Keep an eye on things.

35:39.619 --> 35:42.299
See if she still sends you candy

35:43.259 --> 35:44.659
when you're not asking for it.

35:50.540 --> 35:51.139
Right?

35:52.819 --> 35:53.460
Look,

35:53.540 --> 35:55.100
speak of the devil, here's a message from her.

35:59.779 --> 36:01.659
[Dear lawyers, the trial is set for the day after tomorrow.]

36:01.659 --> 36:02.980
[Shall we meet at the court entrance?]

36:03.500 --> 36:04.659
[If you're available tomorrow,]

36:04.659 --> 36:05.380
[come by the law firm.]

36:05.659 --> 36:06.819
[We'll go over some procedures]

36:06.860 --> 36:07.779
[with you.]

36:10.540 --> 36:11.699
Not even a bit curious

36:11.699 --> 36:13.339
about what Ruan Yu said in the group?

36:16.699 --> 36:17.179
[Sure,]

36:17.460 --> 36:18.540
but I have something in the morning.

36:18.940 --> 36:19.460
Lawyer Liu,

36:19.460 --> 36:20.619
when are you available this afternoon?

36:24.139 --> 36:24.900
I need to come early,

36:25.339 --> 36:26.940
I have an appointment later this afternoon.

36:30.659 --> 36:31.299
Xu,

36:32.179 --> 36:32.900
did you grow up

36:32.900 --> 36:34.060
on willpower?

36:36.179 --> 36:37.940
You're clearly curious,

36:38.139 --> 36:39.540
but you won't even glance at your phone.

36:40.259 --> 36:40.779
I made it

36:40.779 --> 36:42.020
very clear from the start.

36:42.819 --> 36:43.779
I'm in charge of preparing the case,

36:44.259 --> 36:45.139
and you're in charge of the court.

36:45.699 --> 36:46.739
Now that my work

36:46.739 --> 36:47.540
is done,

36:48.179 --> 36:50.500
she's your client.

36:52.860 --> 36:54.619
You've been using public resources for personal gain

36:54.619 --> 36:55.420
for so long,

36:55.420 --> 36:57.940
and now you're suddenly being so strict.

36:57.940 --> 36:58.460
Right?

37:00.380 --> 37:02.739
Fine, you're just being stubborn.

37:03.100 --> 37:04.060
Don't trip yourself up.

37:07.339 --> 37:08.380
We have an appointment

37:08.540 --> 37:09.139
I've scheduled a last

37:09.139 --> 37:10.299
pre-trial meeting with Ruan Yu.

37:10.659 --> 37:11.940
This is your last chance

37:11.940 --> 37:13.020
to meet with her.

37:13.619 --> 37:14.940
Don't blame me for not warning you.

37:23.580 --> 37:24.299
Again?

37:24.460 --> 37:25.100
Go on.

37:25.980 --> 37:27.299
Then go easy on me.

37:27.659 --> 37:28.819
Just a few more rounds.

37:32.699 --> 37:33.819
The live broadcast

37:33.819 --> 37:35.739
finally hit 50,000 viewers.

37:35.739 --> 37:36.900
Thanks for everyone's help.

37:41.339 --> 37:44.460
When are you coming back?

37:57.739 --> 37:58.380
Baby,

37:59.299 --> 38:00.580
why are your hands so cold?

38:01.619 --> 38:02.100
Are they?

38:03.460 --> 38:04.259
Let me warm them up for you.

38:16.100 --> 38:16.980
Warm them well.

38:40.900 --> 38:42.139
This wine smells good.

38:45.020 --> 38:45.500
Hello?

38:46.860 --> 38:48.339
[Hello, Mr. Zhang,]

38:48.819 --> 38:50.619
[what are you busy with?]

38:50.779 --> 38:52.380
[Why haven't you replied to my messages?]

38:52.900 --> 38:54.100
Sorry, I was busy

38:54.100 --> 38:54.940
I didn't see your messages.

38:55.659 --> 38:56.139
It's okay.

38:56.259 --> 38:57.139
Are you done now?

38:57.139 --> 38:58.020
I can pick you up.

38:58.580 --> 38:59.060
No need.

38:59.819 --> 39:01.020
There's a celebration banquet at the company.

39:01.020 --> 39:01.779
It's not very convenient.

39:02.259 --> 39:03.100
I'll call you back later.

39:04.420 --> 39:05.779
Alright, you go ahead.

39:10.100 --> 39:11.900
Why are you so official today?

39:13.259 --> 39:15.259
Chuan, did you see that?

39:15.580 --> 39:16.060
That one.

39:16.540 --> 39:17.139
That one.

39:17.699 --> 39:18.860
She's the boss's daughter.

39:37.659 --> 39:38.060
Okay.

39:41.940 --> 39:42.420
Mr. Gao.

39:43.139 --> 39:43.819
Watch out.

39:55.020 --> 39:55.580
It's okay.

39:55.819 --> 39:56.540
Be careful.

39:58.460 --> 39:59.219
Sorry.

40:03.420 --> 40:04.060
Zhang Chuan.

40:10.420 --> 40:11.420
Do you remember me?

40:12.139 --> 40:12.779
Of course.

40:13.339 --> 40:14.580
We met at the company.

40:20.659 --> 40:21.219
Thank you.

40:22.299 --> 40:22.900
You're welcome.

40:25.619 --> 40:26.100
Mr. Gao,

40:26.100 --> 40:26.860
how are you doing lately?

40:27.139 --> 40:27.739
Pretty good.

40:53.699 --> 40:54.380
Mr. Gao,

40:56.060 --> 40:56.940
how are you going to go back?

40:58.540 --> 40:59.500
The driver will take me.

41:02.020 --> 41:02.580
Here.

41:16.619 --> 41:17.779
See you next time, Mr. Gao.

41:25.380 --> 41:26.020
Are you going together?

41:34.940 --> 41:35.580
Be careful.

42:00.339 --> 42:01.659
It's so early.

42:01.659 --> 42:02.900
You're already working?

42:04.500 --> 42:06.179
Are you in such a hurry to see my client?

42:07.900 --> 42:09.139
Weren't you still stubborn yesterday?

42:09.500 --> 42:10.380
Have you thought it through?

42:12.380 --> 42:13.779
It seems that last night,

42:13.779 --> 42:14.940
my efforts to accompany you

42:15.980 --> 42:16.900
weren't in vain.

42:23.060 --> 42:23.980
What are you looking at?

42:26.739 --> 42:27.420
Haven't you prepared

42:27.420 --> 42:28.659
the court materials for Ruan Yu?

42:29.460 --> 42:30.580
That's your job.

42:31.940 --> 42:33.380
Even if it is,

42:33.380 --> 42:35.100
why are you looking at these?

42:35.100 --> 42:35.980
This is a divorce case

42:35.980 --> 42:36.540
from years ago.

42:36.540 --> 42:38.420
The parties have already remarried,

42:38.540 --> 42:39.580
and their child is three years old.

42:39.580 --> 42:40.659
You're still looking at it?

42:41.219 --> 42:42.619
Checking the filing status.

42:42.860 --> 42:44.580
All of these.

42:46.380 --> 42:48.020
You slept at the office after playing basketball yesterday?

42:50.819 --> 42:52.940
No wonder they say when love fails,

42:53.259 --> 42:54.020
career thrives.

42:54.739 --> 42:55.819
With your work ethic,

42:57.139 --> 42:58.060
how could you not succeed?

42:58.860 --> 42:59.860
You just

42:59.860 --> 43:00.900
have too much energy

43:01.179 --> 43:02.259
and nowhere to channel it.

43:03.980 --> 43:04.500
This afternoon,

43:04.500 --> 43:05.980
we have pre-trial coaching.

43:06.219 --> 43:07.339
Don't you need to prepare?

43:09.540 --> 43:10.819
Alright, then I'll...

43:10.940 --> 43:13.460
Thank you, Lawyer Xu, for your tireless efforts,

43:14.100 --> 43:15.659
sacrificing your own rest time

43:15.779 --> 43:16.980
to help your colleagues

43:16.980 --> 43:17.900
for the firm.

43:18.380 --> 43:20.020
I was too narrow-minded.

43:21.500 --> 43:22.060
Goodbye.

43:24.139 --> 43:25.179
You've been watching

43:25.179 --> 43:25.940
too much "Splendid Times".

43:26.420 --> 43:27.580
That drama is really good.

43:34.179 --> 43:34.900
Lawyer Liu,

43:35.699 --> 43:36.659
is Lawyer Xu not

43:36.860 --> 43:38.100
attending the meeting today?

43:38.819 --> 43:40.060
Yes, he has a

43:40.060 --> 43:41.060
case to handle.

43:41.380 --> 43:41.980
Don't worry.

43:42.060 --> 43:43.259
I've already reviewed

43:43.259 --> 43:44.540
all the materials on your side.

43:46.540 --> 43:47.100
It's okay.

43:51.699 --> 43:52.339
You don't...

43:52.339 --> 43:53.619
Next time, I won't have time

43:53.619 --> 43:54.819
to attend the pre-trial coaching.

43:54.819 --> 43:55.619
This is the last time.

43:58.500 --> 43:59.460
The last time.

44:05.219 --> 44:06.020
Okay, okay.

44:06.619 --> 44:08.179
The last time.

44:11.420 --> 44:13.100
I only printed two copies of this document.

44:20.259 --> 44:21.659
How about you two share one?

44:23.860 --> 44:24.460
No, thanks.

44:24.460 --> 44:25.739
I'll just take a picture of it with my phone.

44:25.860 --> 44:27.380
No, that's not a good idea.

44:27.659 --> 44:29.100
It's fine, just take one.

44:29.580 --> 44:30.580
We'll take one.

44:35.219 --> 44:36.420
You didn't find a chance before,

44:36.580 --> 44:37.980
and now that there's a chance, you don't take it.

44:38.380 --> 44:39.540
You've really been hit hard.

44:45.219 --> 44:46.380
Then let's get started.

44:47.179 --> 44:48.339
With two lawyers here,

44:49.020 --> 44:49.779
I believe

44:49.779 --> 44:51.060
we'll win this case.

44:51.779 --> 44:52.739
Don't be too optimistic.

44:53.380 --> 44:55.380
Before the court's final judgment,

44:55.819 --> 44:56.500
no one can

44:56.500 --> 44:57.460
guarantee

44:57.699 --> 44:58.980
the result with certainty.

44:59.460 --> 45:01.219
Lawyer Xu, could there

45:01.219 --> 45:02.619
be any unexpected developments in this case?

45:06.219 --> 45:06.900
Here's the thing,

45:07.259 --> 45:08.619
evidence ambushes

45:08.619 --> 45:09.179
do happen,

45:09.380 --> 45:12.100
but they're rare.

45:12.219 --> 45:13.380
If that does happen,

45:13.420 --> 45:14.020
don't worry,

45:14.420 --> 45:15.739
I can handle it.

45:16.779 --> 45:18.460
Don't be intimidated

45:18.460 --> 45:19.020
by Lawyer Xu's words.

45:19.420 --> 45:20.259
He's been

45:20.500 --> 45:21.619
dealing with some issues lately

45:23.380 --> 45:24.500
and is quite pessimistic.

45:25.819 --> 45:27.380
If Attorney Liu could cut the chatter,

45:28.100 --> 45:29.619
I might feel a bit more optimistic.

45:36.860 --> 45:37.940
Let's get started.

45:47.540 --> 45:48.219
That's basically

45:48.219 --> 45:49.179
the situation of your case.

45:49.339 --> 45:51.020
Ruan Yu, if you have

45:51.020 --> 45:52.219
any other questions,

45:52.779 --> 45:54.060
you can ask Lawyer Xu.

45:59.259 --> 45:59.779
No need.

46:00.500 --> 46:01.940
Lawyer Liu, you've already

46:01.940 --> 46:03.100
explained everything very clearly.

46:17.540 --> 46:18.179
I'll be on my way now.

46:19.339 --> 46:19.940
Lawyer Xu,

46:24.259 --> 46:25.699
it was raining heavily yesterday,

46:25.940 --> 46:26.940
and I was in a hurry to get off,

46:27.540 --> 46:29.020
so I didn't get a chance to thank you.

46:30.779 --> 46:31.819
Thank you for giving me a ride home.

46:33.619 --> 46:34.299
It's on my way.

46:35.699 --> 46:36.299
Wait.

47:14.139 --> 47:14.779
Happy graduation.

47:16.460 --> 47:17.060
And

47:19.179 --> 47:19.699
goodbye.
